            f"📋 Gists    : {gists}\n"
            f"👥 Followers: {followers}\n"
            f"➡️ Following: {following}\n\n"
            f"📅 Joined   : {h(created)}\n"
            f"🔗 Profile  : {profile}\n\n"
            f"<tg-emoji emoji-id='6147464060305676048'>😎</tg-emoji> DEV @Shuvobhai ✅"
